_[Habla Costa Rica [es]](http://hablacostarica.com/caminata-anti-mineria-de-
san-jose-a-crucitas/)_ reports on a march against mining which will start July
12 and end July 18. The march was organized by a group of citizens under the
name “Coordinadora Ni una sola mina” (Coordination Not One Single Mine) _._
The blog post includes a schedule of the march (including corresponding
locations), and a statement by the organizers.

